1)install perl
2)download openssl https://www.openssl.org/source/

in vs native tools x86

perl Configure VC-WIN32 --prefix=C:\Build-OpenSSL-VC-32 no-asm
ms\do_ms
nmake -f ms\nt.mak            (ntdll.mak if need dll build)
nmake -f ms\nt.mak install    (ntdll.mak if need dll build)







X64

perl Configure VC-WIN64A --prefix=C:\Build-OpenSSL-VC-64 no-asm
ms\do_win64a
nmake -f ms\nt.mak
nmake -f ms\nt.mak install
